Now that you mention it though, I'm seeing other connections (25A, 42A, and 50A) but that's because I have the mind of a teenage boy.

@Beth

Well, I do sometimes take things further, like on a Monday several months ago that featured 24 (if I remember correctly) proper nouns. That really did seem like a very poor choice for a Monday puzzle, and I blamed the editor for it - not the constructor though.

I make it very clear also because I used to get flak when I did not do that. I presumed it was obvious a comment on a board such as this is personal and only reflects a single person's opinion. I did not spell out the fact every time I posted. Many people got offended, claiming I was speaking for them and they resented that. So now I pepper my posts with personallys, IMOs, etc.

