I also don't really understand the general premise of your post. I don't "complain" about any unknown entry when I can get it with crosses. I report in my comments on not personally enjoying two or more unknowns crossing. When a brand crosses a person's name, and neither is as simple as Coca Cola or Jane, I will be stumped - and understandably so.

